# UI Patterns

## Save/Action Buttons
- Always place the save/submit button in the **page header**, aligned to the right
- Always use an **icon** alongside button text (e.g. Save icon + "Save")
- Never place action buttons at the bottom of a form
- Use the `form` attribute to link the header button to the form below

## Required Fields
- Show a red asterisk (*) next to required field labels
- On submit, invalid fields get: red border, shake animation, error message below
- Clear the error state as soon as the user starts interacting with the field

## Field Design
- Minimal: transparent background, subtle border, uppercase small label
- Autosave on detail/edit pages (debounced 600ms)
- Create pages use explicit save button in header

## Icons
- Always use Lucide icons
- Buttons should always have an icon + text (never text-only)
